{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1e77ec596a","title":"迅速弃灭聊城等处伪军","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d70f9949c3","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":15,"articleId":"1e77ec596a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"450b180d96","type":"paragraph","text":"迅速弃灭聊城等处伪军口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1e77ec596a"},{"id":"d358875c21","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年6月15日）陈、舒，刘、邓、薄聊城伪军三千及高唐、博平、禹城间伪军万余必须迅速肃清。除晋要鲁像出兵一万五干外，望陈舒令海出兵一万以上，迅速出动，归刘邓薄统一指挥，消灭该，以除后惠，而利尔后之作战。望刘邓薄立即任命此战役的统一指挥机关，进行各项准备，争取于本月底下月初消灭该。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1e77ec596a"},{"id":"1bd6babe14","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1e77ec596a"},{"id":"52dd5da33b","type":"paragraph","text":"已删[1]1946年6月中旬，晋鲁豫军区拟发起聊（城）高（唐）禹（）战役，建议满海军区出兵1万予以配合。这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给新四军军长兼山东平区司令员陈数、政治部主任舒同和香党普豫军区司令","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1e77ec596a"}],"page":{"id":"1b6966bc49","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1e77ec596a","start":388,"end":388}}}},"__N_SSG":true}